sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as regex-detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes<br/>kubelet

    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: PII Detection Request

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Body: {contents: [...], detector_params: {regex: [...]}}
    Note right of Detector: Resolve detector names:<br/>• "email" → built-in regex<br/>• "ssn" → built-in regex<br/>• "credit-card" → built-in regex<br/>• other → compile as raw regex

    Note right of Detector: Scan each content item<br/>against all regex patterns

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Body: [[{start, end, text, detection, detection_type, score}]]

    Note over K8s,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    K8s->>Detector: GET /health<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Detector-->>K8s: 200 OK<br/>Body: "healthy"
